{"tid":312948,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙法庭接納美斯以25萬歐羅代替監禁","createTime":"2017-07-08T02:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T02:59:47.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"743a17ce1d9ed7a893533344f82481468c073c85","tid":312948,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.playbuzz.com/cdn/fcfa148b-a134-46dd-b664-8c710aaceaec/4c3f2fa6-3d3d-4d82-834c-4b42ccbf0b52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.playbuzz.com%2Fcdn%2Ffcfa148b-a134-46dd-b664-8c710aaceaec%2F4c3f2fa6-3d3d-4d82-834c-4b42ccbf0b52.jpg&h=66303e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠鐘埋單找數喇！效力巴塞隆拿嘅阿根廷球王美斯同佢老竇佐治美斯，周六凌晨正式收到西班牙法庭通知，佢哋原本因為逃稅而分別被罰嘅21個月同15個月刑期，依家只要分別繳交額外嘅25萬2千歐元(約224萬港元)同18萬歐元(約160萬港元)罰款，就可以以錢代監，即係唔使坐囉！雖然話呢個世界真係好似有錢大晒，不過美斯父子就唔係話有特權，事關根據西班牙法例，凡刑期少於24個月而又係初犯者，的而且確係可以用錢嚟代坐監，你有冇佢哋符囉！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170708/bkn-20170708024845279-0708_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170708%2Fbkn-20170708024845279-0708_00882_001.html&d=LwiE9fft%2Bjh3yZ3OrvFOrdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=e78b13aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170708/bkn-20170708024845279-0708_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f508a0a89933cc8354b36d4d920d1f3b226ba2cd","tid":312948,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"知錯能改 真心欣賞"},{"pid":"12ec846e164094f5f4d0000478e89dded8384fca","tid":312948,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"難怪有堆人懷念<br />\n<br />\n薩拉查<br />\n佛朗哥<br />\n<br />\n年代<br />\n<br />\n反正都係偏有錢人 有權勢人"},{"pid":"0f2309e7bcfe10448701a38fc6833aea184d917c","tid":312948,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"如果加泰獨立左可能就要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\